  "title": "2026-1학기 한국인-외국인 학생 융화 프로그램 참가자 모집(~04/13)",
  "category": "비교과프로그램",
  "published_at": "2026-04-08",
  "detail_url": "https://www.dongguk.edu/article/INTSTUNOTICE/detail/26764267",
  "content_text": "한\n국인 학생과 외국인 유학생간의 문화체험 프로그램을 시행하고자 하니 관심 있는 학생들의 많은 신청 바랍니다.\n1. 프로그램 안내\n가.\n일시 :\n2026.4.24.(\n금), 19:00~22:00\n나.\n장소 : 대학로 올웨이즈시어터\n다.\n프로그램 : 연극 [불편한 편의점] 관람\n※ 본 연극은 한국어로 진행됩니다. 한국어 이해에 어려움이 있는 학생은 추후 다른 프로그램에 지원해 주시기 바랍니다.\n라. 참가비 : 무료\n2. 신청 방법\n가.\n신청 기간 :\n2026.04.08.(\n수) ~ 2026.04.15.(수)\n나.\n선발 인원 : 40명 (한국인 20명, 외국인 20명)\n다.\n신청 방법 :\n네이버폼\n☞\n클릭하여 신청하기\n라.\n선발 결과 :\n04.17.(금\n) 신청서에 기재된 연락처로 안내 예정\n3.\n참가 혜택 : DreamPATH\n마일리지 지급(10점)\n4.\n유의사항\n가.\n신청자가 많을 경우,\n조기 마감될 수 있습니다.\n나.\n당일 불참 시 추후 문화체험 및 행사에 참여가 제한됩니다.\n다.\n추후 개인사정으로 참여하지 못할 경우 사전에 반드시 연락바랍니다.\n5.\n문의사항 :\n글로벌학생팀 (02-2260-4947,\nscf@dongguk.edu\n)\n​",
  "content_html": "<p>\n\n</p><p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">한<span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">국인 학생과 외국인 유학생간의 문화체험 프로그램을 시행하고자 하니 관심 있는 학생들의 많은 신청 바랍니다.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">1. 프로그램 안내</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">가. </span>일시 : <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">2026.4.24.(</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">금), 19:00~22:00</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">나. </span>장소 : 대학로 올웨이즈시어터</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">다. </span>프로그램 : 연극 [불편한 편의점] 관람</span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">  </span></span></strong>※ 본 연극은 한국어로 진행됩니다. 한국어 이해에 어려움이 있는 학생은 추후 다른 프로그램에 지원해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">라. 참가비 : 무료</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">2. 신청 방법</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">가. </span>신청 기간 : <span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">2026.04.08.(</span>수) ~ 2026.04.15.(수)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">나. </span>선발 인원 : 40명 (한국인 20명, 외국인 20명)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">다. </span>신청 방법 : <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">네이버폼 </span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\">☞</span><a href=\"https://naver.me/GJZl75Tr\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFFF00;\"> </span><span style=\"white-space: pre;\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFFF00;\">클릭하여 신청하기</span></span></a></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">라. </span>선발 결과 : <u style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">04.17.(금</u><u>) 신청서에 기재된 연락처로 안내 예정</u></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">3. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">참가 혜택 : DreamPATH </span>마일리지 지급(10점)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">4. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">유의사항</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:13.5pt;line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">가. </span>신청자가 많을 경우, </span>조기 마감될 수 있습니다.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">나. </span>당일 불참 시 추후 문화체험 및 행사에 참여가 제한됩니다.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\">  <span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">다. </span>추후 개인사정으로 참여하지 못할 경우 사전에 반드시 연락바랍니다.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">5. </span></span><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\">문의사항 : </span>글로벌학생팀 (02-2260-4947, </span><a href=\"mailto:scf@dongguk.edu\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-line: none;\">scf@dongguk.edu</span></span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:20.95pt;box-sizing:border-box;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;widows:2;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:돋움체;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">​</span><img alt=\"ㅎ눃ㅇ뇨룜녈\" src=\"/cmmn/fileView?path=/ckeditor//INTSTUNOTICE&amp;physical=1775616695687.png&amp;contentType=image\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 553px;\"/></span></span></p>",
